        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>A sealed connector kit is available to improve the quality of the electrical connection for the
                    cab harness to the underseat heater box. The Metri-Pack connector will replace the Series 56 Packard
                    connector. The Metri-Pack connector offers an environmentally sealed connector with improved blade
                    stabilization and alignment during mating. If the Packard Series 56 connector shows evidence of
                    corrosion, high resistance, or heat stress, the connector should be replaced.
                </para>
                <para>Conventional 9000 Models built before February 12, 1992, and cabover 9000 Models built before
                    February 7, 1992 use connector kit 2500583C91. Conventional 9000 Models built after February 12,
                    1992, and cabover 9000 Models built after February 7, 1992 use connector kit 2500582C91.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
